<i>noun</i>: 화두 [화두] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>화두 [화두]</dt><br>
<dd>1. topic; subject; talking point</dd><br>
<dd>이야기의 첫머리.</dd><br>
<dd>Literally meaning the head of a story, the topic of a conversation or speech, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. topic</dd><br>
<dd>관심을 두어 중요하게 생각하거나 이야기할 만한 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An important subject that is worth thinking or talking about with interest.</dd><br>
<dd>3. keyword</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서, 수행을 하는 사람이 깨달음을 얻기 위한 실마리로 삼는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>In Buddhism, literally meaning the head of a story, a word or phrase used by an ascetic as a clue to reach spiritual enlightenment.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>